Paper: hep-th/0206232

Date: 2002-06-26

Title: Toward Construction of Exact Operator Solution of $A_N$-Toda Field

TheoryAuthors: Y. Takimoto, T. Fujiwara

Comments: 11 pages, latex, no figures

Quantum $A_N$-Toda field theory in two dimensions is investigated based onthe method of quantizing canonical free field. Toda exponential operatorassociated with the fundamental weight $\lambda^1$ is constructed.